text: The Philippine Sea is the body of water east of the Philippines and Taiwan. It is a part of the western end of the Pacific Ocean. The Philippine Sea is bounded by china Japan to the north, the Marianas to the east and Palau to the south. ==Geology== It straddles on the Philippine Plate.International Association for Earthquake Engineering.
